body_html:
Those are informational log messages that are emitted during startup. They do not indicate any code is actually running via XLA.

Try setting the environment variable TF_CPP_MIN_VLOG_LEVEL=2 and looking for log messages from xla_device_launch_op.cc or xla_local_launch_op.cc.
